default3.2.
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultSimilarly, no 
defaultoxo
default-degradable bags are produced in the UK, instead they are mainly manufactured in the Far East along with most other plastic bags through a licensing system for third party production
default. On this basis, it is unlikely that an exemption for 
defaultoxo
default-biodegradable bags will lead to job creation in the UK.
